  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 375°F (190°C).",
    "Bake the sweet potatoes for 45-60 minutes, or until tender.",
    "In a large bowl, combine the flour, brown sugar, and salt.",
    "Add the melted butter, eggs, and vanilla extract to the bowl.",
    "Using a fork, mash the sweet potatoes and add them to the bowl.",
    "Mix the ingredients together until well combined.",
    "Transfer the mixture to a 9x13 inch baking dish.",
    "Top with marshmallows.",
    "Bake for an additional 10-15 minutes, or until the marshmallows are golden brown.",
    "Serve warm."
